ons of seegSDM and seegMBG from GitHub\nfor (i in 1:length(github)) {\n  devtools::install_github(names(github)[i], ref = github[i])\n}\n\nmessage('\\nPackage installation done')\nreportTime()\nmessage('\\n\\n')\n",
